Besides, Imagine that Luclin had been released on some kind of &quot;Legends&quot; server 6 months ago, and it was being prepared for release to the live servers now, with months of testing on a huge scale first....would you rather get a buggy product first, or a program that runs smoothly cause it was beta tested on a bunch of rich lab rats?  If they want to pay $40/mo so that I dont have to reboot everytime I go Linkdead, GREAT!!  <br>
<br>
Sorry for the rant, but For those people who are cussing out sony/verant, remember what a good thing you have got, and don't worry about what you don't.<br>
<br>
Kypreos Taidaishir<br>
21st Paladin of the Commonlands<br>
