<br>
I'm going to stop now since I know they'll be reactions saying I don't &quot;understand business&quot;, well I do...<br>
<br>
I know the everquest current role... and the role I'll be playing when an alternative comes that I enjoy...<br>
<br>
Unless they surprise me and turn it around again...<br>
